<% title 'Gamocosm About' %>
<% content_for :meta_description, 'Gamocosm is FOSS. It makes it easy to host Minecraft servers for friends.' %>
<% meta_keywords ['Minecraft', 'hosting', 'open source', 'cloud', 'Digital Ocean', 'per-hour'] %>
<div class="row">
	<div class="col-sm-12">
		<h1>About</h1>
		<p>
			Gamocosm is FOSS.
			Gamocosm doesn't accept payment, no ads, and no tracking user data.
			I pay for all the development and production costs out of my pocket.
			I do this because I want to make something useful.
			I'll accept donations later if costs start being an issue.
			I intend to keep everything as transparent as possible.
			<%= link_to 'More information on how Gamocosm works', info_path %>.
		</p>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="row">
	<div class="col-sm-12">
		<h2>Contact</h2>
		<ul>
			<li>Submit an issue on <%= link_to 'GitHub', issues_path %> (the most reliable way!)</li>
			<li>Reddit PM "raekye"</li>
			<li>IRC in <code>#gamocosm</code> on <code>irc.esper.net</code> (<%= link_to 'web chat', irc_path %>) (<%= link_to 'chat history', irc_history_path %>)</li>
			<li>Yes IRC is easy, but the best way to contact me is through GitHub or Reddit!</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="row">
	<div class="col-sm-12">
		<h2>Source</h2>
		<p>The source code is on <%= link_to 'GitHub', source_path %>. Feel free to fork and send a pull request!</p>
	</div>
</div>
